{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act29side_level_act29side_09_beg","storyGroup":"act29side","storySort":19,"storyDependence":"act29side_level_act29side_08_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"ZT-9","storyName":"幻想曲“赠答” ","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act29side/level_act29side_09_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act29side_09","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":17,"next":19,"characters":["黑键","“巫王的余音”？","愤怒的路人？","乌提卡领民？","别格勒？","巫王","？？？","弗莱蒙特","赫尔昏佐伦"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8c/Avg_bg_44_g10_endlessspiral.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spirlstrsndlss","volume":"1","id":6},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_energywell","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":7},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_openftstpwalk","volume":"1","id":12},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"......","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#13$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"费德里科先生？薇薇安娜女士？","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c1/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":17},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#13$1","focus":"n","id":18},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bodyfallvalley","volume":"1","id":19},{"type":"text","text":"黑键不清楚自己是何时与其他人走散的，头顶不时有断裂的结构物砸落，脚下的阶梯扭曲而无穷尽。","id":20},{"type":"text","text":"他只能向前。他孑然一身，不知疲倦。","id":21},{"type":"dialog","id":22},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_openftstpwalk","volume":"1","id":23},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":24},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"charslot","id":27},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8c/Avg_bg_44_g10_endlessspiral.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":28},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":29},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":30},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":31},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":32,"musicid":0},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.7","duration":"1","id":33},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1126_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.7","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"黑键，你如此可耻。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"你干扰了我们的判断，浪费了我们的时间，拖累了我们的事业，你几乎成为最大的罪人！","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"charslot","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"那还真是抱歉啊。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":41},{"type":"charslot","id":42},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bdevilmgc","volume":"1","id":43},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":44},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_skill_darkholespell","volume":"1","id":45},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_explosion_stone","volume":"0.6","id":48},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":49},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"100","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":50},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":51},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1126_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"你现在想要同去迎接陛下吗？还是企图阻止陛下重新降临尘世？","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"你没有资格，也做不到。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"早该想到的，我们早该想到的。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"明明陛下的血脉如此强大，精神如此坚韧，而尘世之音不过是其乐声的万一，却已经让你痛苦到难以承受。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"你生来孱弱，孱弱得背负不起任何期待。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":59},{"type":"charslot","id":60},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"各位的意思是，你们将这些毫无价值的杂音强塞进我的脑海......","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"到头来，我应该为这件事负责？","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":65},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1126_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"哼，你应该庆幸，黑键。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"如果一开始就知晓尘世之音并非获取陛下遗产的钥匙，那对双子会假模假样地赏赐你乌提卡家族的封地吗？","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"不。甚至等不到那时候，你就会死在襁褓之中。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”？","text":"“乌提卡伯爵”，你应以享有这个封号为荣，更应以享有这个封号为耻！","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1126_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":71},{"type":"charslot","id":72},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"是啊，我也这么想。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"所以，滚开！","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"charslot","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":79},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1126_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":80},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":81},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_skill_darkholespell","volume":"1","id":82},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_smkedspte","volume":"1","id":85},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":86},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.7","duration":"1","id":87},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.7","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":88},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":89},{"type":"charslot","id":90},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的路人？","text":"黑键，你如此可恨。","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的路人？","text":"多少人因巫王的暴政横死，多少人不明不白地消失，莱塔尼亚遍体鳞伤，二十三年过去，有些伤口依旧在流血。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的路人？","text":"*莱塔尼亚粗口*！结果那个暴君悄无声息地死在了一个夜晚，甚至没有得到任何应有的惩罚！","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的路人？","text":"而你是他在这个世上唯一的后裔，你生来就带着罪孽的血腥味，你该代他赎罪！代他向整个莱塔尼亚忏悔！","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的路人？","text":"黑键，你有什么资格，一边过着养尊处优的生活，一边自嘲着“自己明明谁也不是”？","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"我同你们一样，没有一天不在痛恨这罪孽的血！","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌提卡领民？","text":"不，你压根不清楚它到底引诱了多少罪恶！那些残党一次次潜入乌提卡领，围着你的高塔打转，像嗅到了腐肉的苍蝇。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_493_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌提卡领民？","text":"我的小儿子才刚进治安队当差，就因为发现了他们的踪迹，尸体在水沟里漂了三天才被发现。而你永远躲在高塔上！","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_493_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌提卡领民？","text":"你甚至不知道乌提卡领到底有多大，出产什么作物，首都的税务官一年来几趟，这几年领地又遭受了什么灾害。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_493_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌提卡领民？","text":"没有比你更可恨的领主，伯爵大人。","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_493_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"......","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"charslot","id":107},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","focus":"n","duration":"0","id":108},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","focus":"l","duration":"0","id":109},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":110},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_skill_darkholeborn","volume":"1","id":111},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_smkedspte","volume":"1","id":114},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":115},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":116},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":117},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":118},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1","id":119},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":120},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":121},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":122},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","text":"","id":123},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":124},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","text":"","id":125},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_486_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.7","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"停下来，别再往前了。现在的你，越英勇越像个笑话。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"黑键，你如此可悲。","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"还记得格特鲁德吗？她死前曾留下最恶毒的诅咒，诅咒维谢海姆、诅咒莱塔尼亚、诅咒巫王......她也诅咒了你。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"她诅咒你“永远无法摆脱血脉中的疯狂”。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"你回到崔林特尔梅的时候，我在想，该死，这个疯女人的诅咒真的应验了，倔强的孩子终究无法挣脱命运的漩涡。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"他当然不会顺应命运，但这一次，他无可避免地要为挣脱它而陷入疯狂。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"......你应该感到轻松，不是吗？","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"尘世之音困扰了你十多年，与其说你一直在竭力抵抗，不如说你在小心翼翼地看守着它。","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"守着一枚炸弹，害怕它随时会被引爆，害怕它被有心之人利用，戕害到无辜的生命。","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"这是你沉重但意义非凡的......命运。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"可既然它只是杂音，只是并不致命的头痛......回去吧，黑键。格特鲁德的诅咒失败了。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"不！","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"我不能接受！","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_486_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"因为这是一种更加残忍的诅咒？","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"到头来，你的努力不值一提，你的反抗毫无意义。那些为此而牺牲的人，那些你决定永生铭记的眼泪和笑容......","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"你要如何去面对？","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"你突然发现，信任、怜惜、理解、彼此托付......那些无比美好的情感，原来并不因稀少而珍贵。","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"它们一下子变得轻飘飘的......","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"别格勒？","text":"像是一个玩笑。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_486_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":148},{"type":"charslot","id":149},{"type":"subtitle","text":"是啊，玩笑。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":150},{"type":"subtitle","text":"它们怎么能，只是一个玩笑？！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":151},{"type":"subtitle","id":152},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_486_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":153},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_skill_darkholeboost","volume":"1","id":154},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":157},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_smkedspte","volume":"1","id":158},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":159},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$1","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":160},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":161},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":163},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":164},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":165},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":167},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":168},{"type":"charslot","id":169},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_bg_44_g11_thronesworld.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":170},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":171},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dimnlspamb","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":172},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":173},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":175},{"type":"text","text":"他看见了高塔。","id":176},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"哈哈，果然。我知道你就在里面。","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"哪怕死去了这么久，你还是妄想让这座邪恶的高塔重新降临在莱塔尼亚。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"你不会得逞！","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"我会施展所有的法术，我会挥动法杖直至它折断，我会运转源石骰子直至它碎成齑粉。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"如果你还有血肉，我就摧毁你的血肉。如果你还有魂灵，我就湮灭你的魂灵。","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"我要质问你诅咒你唾骂你，我要杀死你。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"——巫王！","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":190},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":191},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":192},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":193},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":195},{"type":"background","id":196},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":197},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":198},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.15","fadetime":"2","id":199},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.15","fadetime":"2","id":200},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_act29side_sys_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act29side/m_act29side_sys_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":201,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":202},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_44_i12_1.png","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","y":"300","fadetime":"1.5","id":203},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-400","xTo":"200","duration":"35","block":"false","id":204},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巫王","text":"弗朗茨。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巫王","text":"别去碰空气中的音符。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巫王","text":"被我删去的这部分旋律，其中融合的术式在完全逸散前仍有可怖的力量。","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巫王","text":"平复你的情绪，回避千年前先贤们的意志，别让自己的心神被牵引......","id":209},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_44_i12_1.png","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","x":"400","y":"100","fadetime":"3","id":211},{"type":"imagetween","xTo":"0","duration":"40","block":"false","id":212},{"type":"text","text":"黑键攥紧法杖，但他说不出哪怕一个字。","id":213},{"type":"text","text":"他曾读过所有关于巫王的文献，甚至不久前还被囚禁在这个房间，他当然知晓这段历史。","id":214},{"type":"text","text":"音符在房间内缓缓流淌，名为“叙拉古”的旋律正在离开“莱塔尼亚”的大乐章。","id":215},{"type":"text","text":"他仿佛听见了巨大的雷、连绵的雨和浩荡的风，“莱塔尼亚的意志”化作与天地等同的伟力，反复冲刷着这个不大的房间。","id":216},{"type":"text","text":"仅仅站在门口，澎湃的能量便死死压住了他的心跳。","id":217},{"type":"dialog","id":218},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.15","fillto":"0","fadetime":"3","id":219},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.15","fillto":"0","fadetime":"3","id":220},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_44_i12_1.png","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3","id":221},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.05","yScaleFrom":"1.05","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"10","block":"false","id":222},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":223},{"type":"text","text":"房间中央的人并未回头看他，那个人是如此专注，又是如此傲然。惊涛骇浪中，他是那块永远高出浪头的礁石。","id":224},{"type":"text","text":"黑键不由得怀疑自己来错了地方，这里仿佛是某个作曲家宿命的夜晚，或者历史学者最激昂的课堂。","id":225},{"type":"text","text":"这里没有他的仇，没有他的命，他的愤怒无地自容。","id":226},{"type":"text","text":"黑键突然意识到一件事：他回想过往的全部人生，哪怕在那些最为恐怖的噩梦里——","id":227},{"type":"text","text":"自己其实从未真正见过巫王。","id":228},{"type":"dialog","id":229},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"image","id":233},{"type":"charslot","id":234},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_bg_44_g7_ludwigsuniv_inside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":235},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":236},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"弗莱蒙特，你又迟到了。","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我不记得你是个受欢迎的老师，你也会被学生围住没法脱身吗？","id":239},{"type":"dialog","id":240},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":241},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":243},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$2","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"......","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"第一，如果因施教者的脾气而在知识面前却步，说明这群号称莱塔尼亚最优秀的年轻人日后也只配给高塔清清苔藓。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"第二，每个月给我发放学者津贴的是路德维格大学，所以我似乎没有必要被你召之即来。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#9$2","focus":"l","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"我是不是不该跟赫尔昏佐伦陛下顶嘴？","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":251},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":252},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":253},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"......","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"你也不是第一次了。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"下个月，各大区的选帝侯便会陆续到达维杜尼亚，我们剩的时间不多，弗莱蒙特。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"我希望他们觐见结束时，能将更新之后的金律乐章副本带回各自的大区。","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#9$2","focus":"l","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"你已经是那些鹿和羊口中千年一遇的明君了，就这么急着巩固自己的威信？","id":260,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"下一步是什么，将选帝侯们的军队和行政权力收归宫廷的高塔？","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"我们讨论过这个问题。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"我刚到莱塔尼亚那时候，当时的皇帝就在头疼叙拉古的问题。这都过去多久了？","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"那些狼崽子们如今也只敢搞些大一点的小动作。","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"你才刚刚即位，不如多花点时间挑挑大典上要穿的华服。","id":268,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"挑好了。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#8$2","focus":"l","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"......","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-8$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#7$2","focus":"r","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"你仍在担心，改写金律乐章，以及后续的一系列国策，可能会让整个国家陷入不可知的动乱？","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#5$2","focus":"l","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"我并不关心莱塔尼亚，但带着图书馆到处搬家确实麻烦得很。","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"从当上恩瓦德大区选帝侯开始，你就在研究这乐章，我们都清楚它到底是怎么回事，为什么千年来，没人想过也没人能修改它。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#6$2","focus":"l","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"将三大篇章、十重旋律编织成一体的，与其说是音乐的动机或者主题，不如说是千年前那些源石技艺大师融注而成的超级术式......","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"是莱塔尼亚创建之初，无数先贤对这个国家的伟大创造、思考与护佑。是“莱塔尼亚的无上意志”。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#5$2","focus":"l","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"它无限接近于永恒。","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"“永恒”？","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"除了米诺斯那帮喜欢在白墙下讨论“人能否两次踏入同一条河流”的哲学家，恐怕只有巫妖才喜欢用这个词。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"也唯有你们才理解这个词的含义。","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#6$2","focus":"r","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"“永恒”——不更不易，不移不改。但永恒不等于不朽。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/05/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"诚然，构建乐章的先贤们在千年前完成了难以企及的伟业。","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/05/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"“莱塔尼亚”从那时成为这个国家的名，又不仅是国家的名。","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/05/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"“莱塔尼亚”让这片土地上的万民共荣辱，“莱塔尼亚”将典雅、和谐、道德与美镌刻在了我们的每一次呼吸。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/05/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"他们在千年之前就对这个国度做出了最优的展望与规划，他们让“莱塔尼亚”成了这片土地上的真理。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/05/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"但所有的真理都会朽坏，叙拉古的离心离德便是最好的证明。","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#3$2","focus":"r","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"而我，将为莱塔尼亚带来一个更好的未来。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-3$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":297},{"type":"charslot","id":298},{"type":"text","text":"莱塔尼亚的新君主取出怀中的乐章，侧头看向巫妖。","id":299},{"type":"text","text":"“永恒”“不朽”......","id":300},{"type":"text","text":"赫尔昏佐伦说话的声音并不重，但弗莱蒙特清晰地听见这些宏大的词语在他唇齿间破碎、重组。","id":301},{"type":"dialog","id":302},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"n","id":303},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#4$2","focus":"l","id":304},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":305},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#9$2","focus":"l","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"很狂妄，很“赫尔昏佐伦”。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#5$2","focus":"l","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"但你如何保证，莱塔尼亚在你手中不会遭遇更大的危机，你所谓的未来能够不朽？","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"没有乐章不可被改写，没有法术不可被超越，没有意志不可被战胜，没有未知不可被征服......","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"不朽，在于“更新”。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"时至今日，海洋与天空仍被笼罩在认知的迷雾中，大地便是泰拉人所感所知的极限。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#3$2","focus":"r","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"可根据你分享的知识，连最高的云层、最深的海底，也不过是被时间与空间囚禁的“实在”。","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-3$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"而在实在之外，存在着世界的另一面，虚无、诡谲而危险的未知之境。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-3$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"如若问题无尽，说明答案无尽。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#4$2","focus":"r","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"乌提卡的伯爵塔过于矮小，所以我在维杜尼亚建起始源之塔，它已是莱塔尼亚最高的建筑。但未必是整片大地最高的建筑......","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"我永不停止，这是我与历代先贤的区别。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"这就是我的“不朽”，弗莱蒙特。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#9$2","focus":"l","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"希望你再建一座新塔的时候，房间能多些，这样不至于修改一份乐章还要借用我的密室。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#9$2","focus":"r","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"会的。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"......","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"好了，我们开始吧。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#8$2","focus":"l","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"我去把所有的共振捕捉装置打开，待会儿拆解旋律的时候，能看得更清晰一些。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-8$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":334},{"type":"charslot","id":335},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_mgcdevcstartp","volume":"1","id":336},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":337},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_scroll","volume":"1","id":338},{"type":"text","text":"赫尔昏佐伦在房间中央的椅子上坐稳，凌空铺开乐章，弗莱蒙特则连踢带拽地将各种珍贵的古籍挪至一边，为术式矩阵腾出位置。","id":339},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#8$2","focus":"n","id":340},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"对了，弗莱蒙特，你们如何称呼世界的另一面来着？","id":342,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"（萨卡兹语）“千丝万弦之始终”。","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"很小器的名字。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"“命结”的存在让巫妖这个种族获得了几乎是最为特殊的能力。藏好命结，意味着你们拥有永不终结的生命。","id":347,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#8$2","focus":"r","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"巫妖得以在无限的时间里窥见世界的无限真相，却只是将它们作为知识的一页？","id":349,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-8$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"谨慎是我们的天性。发现越多，宜居的地方越少。","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"那么，弗莱蒙特，你呢？","id":353,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#2$2","focus":"l","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"我？","id":355,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#4$2","focus":"r","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"“千丝万弦之始终”......","id":357,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔昏佐伦","text":"你时常抱怨手底下那些巫妖不是还年轻就是太呆板，却也只是将那个空间当成藏自己命结的抽屉，没想着进去看看？","id":359,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":360},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":362},{"type":"background","id":363},{"type":"charslot","id":364},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/64/Avg_44_i12_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1","id":365},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_golden_star_01","layer":"0","id":366},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_golden_melody_01","layer":"1","id":367},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_golden_melody_02","layer":"2","id":368},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":369},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"text","text":"巨大的寒意席卷弗莱蒙特全身。","id":371},{"type":"text","text":"微小但耀眼的光芒在赫尔昏佐伦法杖的顶端绽开，他已经开始演奏金律乐章，弗莱蒙特手上的动作也未停止。","id":372},{"type":"text","text":"巫妖与卡普里尼，王庭之主与莱塔尼亚皇帝，一直如此默契。","id":373},{"type":"text","text":"再紧张的时刻，两人也能见缝插针讨论几个问题，哲学、音乐，有时候是莱塔尼亚的气候与饮食。","id":374},{"type":"text","text":"赫尔昏佐伦就是如此自然地提到了这件事，提到了真正威胁巫妖生死的，秘密。","id":375},{"type":"text","text":"倘若尽全力施展“放逐”，命弦是否能在一瞬间消解所有音符，将面前这个毫不设防的家伙湮灭在虚空之中？","id":376},{"type":"text","text":"无人知晓莱塔尼亚的新皇帝来到了这里，他有足够的时间知会巫妖王庭从这个国家撤离。","id":377},{"type":"text","text":"但赫尔昏佐伦就是如此自然地提到了这件事，提到了漫长岁月里从来无人发现的，秘密。","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈——","id":379},{"type":"text","text":"良久，弗莱蒙特放声大笑。","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"正好，对那个空间的研究我也碰到了一些瓶颈。","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"赫尔昏佐伦，你要是真的感兴趣......","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"我可以把命结借给你。","id":383},{"type":"dialog","id":384},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magicchange","volume":"1","id":385},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":386},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":387},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":388},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":389},{"type":"bgeffect","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"差不多得了，赫尔昏佐伦。","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"你不觉得怀旧很倒胃口吗，让人想把隔夜饭都吐出来。更何况我还赶时间。","id":392},{"type":"dialog","id":393},{"type":"image","id":394},{"type":"charslot","id":395},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_bg_44_g15_kingsthrone.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":396},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":397},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_churchfire","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"b","id":398},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","channel":"b","fadetime":"2","id":399},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":400},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1116_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巫王","text":"好久不见，弗莱蒙特。","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_1116_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#7$1","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"既然你还记得从我这儿借走了什么，还回来吧。","id":404,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":405},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"b","fadetime":"2","id":406},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":408},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":409},{"type":"charslot","id":410},{"type":"background","id":411},{"type":"image","id":412}],"characters":["黑键","“巫王的余音”？","愤怒的路人？","乌提卡领民？","别格勒？","巫王","？？？","弗莱蒙特","赫尔昏佐伦"]}